videos.description: Kevin Huerter gets the pass on the break and takes flight to punch down a powerful one-handed dunk for the Hawks.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Huerter throws down emphatic fast-break slam) 2021/05/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Huerter throws down emphatic fast-break slam

videos.description: Trae Young pulls up in transition to knock down a deep 3-pointer from the Knicks' logo and gloats to fans in MSG by pointing to the spot where he hit the shot.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Trae gloats after knocking down logo 3) 2021/05/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Trae gloats after knocking down logo 3

videos.description: Trae Young speeds to the basket on the fast break and goes up and under Julius Randle for an impressive reverse layup.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Trae banks in incredibly athletic reverse layup) 2021/05/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Trae banks in incredibly athletic reverse layup

videos.description: Fans at MSG erupt after Julius Randle uses a crafty Eurostep to get around Clint Capela and put in a layup to give the Knicks a 100-91 lead with 1:13 remaining in the game.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Randle sends MSG into a frenzy with dagger bucket) 2021/05/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Randle sends MSG into a frenzy with dagger bucket

videos.description: Obi Toppin's mom can't contain her emotions as she hears the Madison Square Garden crowd chant her son's name after a big dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Obi Toppin's mom gets emotional as MSG chants her son's name) 2021/5/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Obi Toppin's mom gets emotional as MSG chants her son's name

videos.description: Stephen A. Smith praises Knicks fans for creating the electric atmosphere at the Garden and says there will be a ton of New York fans in Atlanta for Games 3 and 4.

videos.headline: Stephen A. after Knicks tie series: We here, it's time

videos.description: Knicks rally from a double-digit deficit to defeat the Hawks and tie up their first-round series.
